### Find bavarian locations in user texts

```elixir
cleaned_note =
  person_df["note"]
  |> S.to_list()
  |> Enum.map(&if(is_binary(&1), do: &1, else: ""))
  |> Enum.map(&Regex.replace(html_r, &1, " "))

